description: Animation and motion tokens for quiz UI
globs: core/ui/**/*.kt,feature/**/*.kt
alwaysApply: false
---

# Animations

- Use `QuizMotion` for selection scale and score counting.
- Use `QuizTokens.selectionSpring` / `scoreSpring` for specs — do not invent new spring configs in features.
- Feedback shake: `Modifier.quizShake()` from `core:ui`.
- List reveals: `AnimatedVisibility` + `fadeIn` / `slideInVertically` on ranking rows.
